RELEASE NOTES:

Driver Magician offers a professional solution for device
drivers backup, restoration, update and removal in
Windows operating system. It identifies all the hardware
in the system, extracts their associated drivers from the
hard disk and backs them up to a location of your
choice. Then when you format and reinstall/upgrade your
operating system, you can restore all the "saved" drivers
just as if you had the original driver diskettes in your
hands. After one system reboot, your PC will be loaded
and running with the required hardware drivers
